gure></p>\n<p>要在移動時有延遲性，是根據這篇 blog 啟發的<br>延遲性-&gt; <strong>transition</strong> 的部分<br><a href=\"https://vocus.cc/article/61bef950fd89780001c95b55\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">[CSS筆記] transition、transform、animation 動畫屬性&gt;</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"遇到的問題\"><a href=\"#遇到的問題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"遇到的問題\"></a>遇到的問題</h2><h3 id=\"問題一\"><a href=\"#問題一\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"問題一\"></a>問題一</h3><p>後來發先照第一個網址的code改，無法達到我想要的成果(九成是我不會改)<br>就看到這個網站 <a href=\"https://www.w3school.com.cn/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">W3school</a> 的 <a href=\"https://www.w3school.com.cn/jquery/event_mouseover.asp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">jQuery 事件 - mouseover() 方法</a><br>之後的程式碼就照它改<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DH5sazj.png\" alt=\"\"><br><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"string\">&quot;p&quot;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">mouseover</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  $(<span class=\"string\">&quot;p&quot;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">css</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;background-color&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;yellow&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">$(<span class=\"string\">&quot;p&quot;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">mouseout</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  $(<span class=\"string\">&quot;p&quot;</span>).<span class=\"title function_\">css</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;background-color&quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;#E9E9E4&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"問題二\"><a href=\"#問題二\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"問題二\"></a>問題二</h3><p>在測試的時候，發現小球在滾動頁面的時候，不會跟著移動<br>接下來就從 <a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/information/js%E8%B7%9F%E9%9A%8F%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">這裡</a> 發現這個 <a href=\"https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1534544?from=15425\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">網站</a></p>\n<p>底下的<br><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"number\">3</span>、<span class=\"keyword\">var</span> Y = ev.<span class=\"property\">clientY</span> + scrollTop; <span class=\"comment\">// 加上了滾動距離</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>可以解決這個問題</p>\n<h1 id=\"完整程式碼\"><a href=\"#完整程式碼\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"完整程式碼\"></a>完整程式碼</h1><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27